svg.script:
<![CDATA[
function showQuestion(text, answer) {
  document.getElementById("questionText").textContent = text;
  document.getElementById("answerText").textContent = answer;
  document.getElementById("answerText").setAttribute("visibility", "hidden");
}
function revealAnswer() {
  document.getElementById("answerText").setAttribute("visibility", "visible");
}
]]>
